title: Dark Cloud OST
description:
The official sound track for the first Dark Cloud game from 2001, including the song in demon shaft which isn&#039;t on the other (dead) torrents (because it was never released on the CD since the japanese version of the game doesn&#039;t include Demon Shaft)

This soooooo nostalgic for me. It was the first video game ever that I owned. I had of course played my friends video games and such, but I had never owned one myself. It was bough together with the ps2 back in -01. Boy have I spent many happy hours with this game ;&#039;)
